nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 174 is the 152nd issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the eighty-second issue published by Titan Magazines. It was released on July 11, 2017. This was the final Star Wars Insider issue to feature Jonathan Wilkins as editor.
Features the very best interviews and articles about the greatest space adventure of all time. Discover amazing features you never knew! Insider is the ultimate guide to the timeless saga!
